    <h1>Autonomous Line-Following Robot</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      A self-navigating two-wheeled robot with PID control and infrared sensing, built entirely from scratch.
    </p>
  </div>
 
  <div class="project-cover">
    <!-- Replace with: <img src="../assets/robot-cover.jpg" alt="Robot on track" /> -->
    🤖
